            <p>
              <strong>Osage County jail visiting hours are Monday through Friday, 9:00 AM to 3:00 PM.</strong> The facility is closed on weekends and holidays. Visitors must be at least 18 years old and present a valid photo ID. Each inmate is limited to one visit per 7-day period, and visits are limited to 30 minutes maximum. These hours are more restrictive than many other Oklahoma counties, so plan accordingly when visiting a loved one.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <input type="checkbox" id="faq2" />
